                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "I don't think there's a bug yet on using the system font sizes, but elliot is moving \nin that direction with his native theme work.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "In general, there's a lot of work to be \ndone to make the graphics scale (tab curves, toolbar buttons, etc) before we can allow \ndifferent font sizes.", 
